    "body": "AbstractMessageHandlerAdapter \r\n\r\nTimeout on synchronous node are not configurable, leading to DDOS of SAM in remote configuration.\r\nfinal void bindSyncNodeServer() {\r\n    node = new SyncNodeServerAdapter(this, 20);\r\n    isBoundToSyncNode = true;\r\n  }\r\na node is waiting  during 20 seconds for the incoming request of the remote client, keeping the SAM busy. \r\nin case of remote connection, a device can break the link without noticing the server. \r\n\r\n",
